en_322835_0	Deputy Minister Buddhika Pathirana says that an insurance scheme for local craftsmen will be introduced this year.
en_322835_1	The Deputy Minister mentioned this while attending the ceremony to open the Palmyrah products village at Vavuniya, Thandikulama area.
en_322835_2	A large number of women will get employment through the village.
en_322835_3	The village has been built with an investment of five million rupees from the National Crafts Council.
